data.description: !!!!  Assumable VA Loan 370k at 2.25% Get a Low Payment !!!!  Great Location in Aurora East Quincy Highlands!!! Solar Panels are paid for free and clear, that means no electric Bill!!!  Cul-De-Sac location, no traffic!! Recently renovated home features New Vinyl Floors on the main Floor!!! New paint in the kitchen and living Room!! New Carpet throughout!! New Granite Counters!! New Plumbing Fixtures and Ceiling Fans!! Newly Painted Large Patio!! 30 Year Warranty on the Windows Replaced in 2021!!  This home has it all!! Move in ready Open House Saturday 9/30/2023 1-3 P.M. Come see it for yourself!
